OL,6,FA farmer from the says his ME
OL,7,Fdiagnosis 'stole his childhood', after
OL,8,Fliving with the debilitating illness
OL,9,Fsince the age of 12.
OL,11,FThomase Cleator lives with myalgic
OL,12,Fencephalomyelitis (ME) while working
OL,13,Fon his family farm in Jurby.
OL,15,FHe said: "Sometimes just coming out is
OL,16,Fenough for what I can do in that day,
OL,17,Fand just getting home again is a
OL,18,Fchallenge".
OL,20,FHe's been sharing his experience of
OL,21,Fliving with ME on the island.
