OL,3,CFarmer says ME 'stole his childhood'
OL,4,Cwhile living in the Isle of Man
OL,6,FThomase was diagnosed with ME when he
OL,7,Fwas 12-years-old.
OL,9,FAt its worst, Thomase would spend many
OL,10,Fdays in bed away from school, struck
OL,11,Fdown with major fatigue and 'painful
OL,12,Fheadaches'.
OL,14,FHe said: "In a sense, I will always
OL,15,Fsay it stole my childhood. Just
OL,16,Fgetting out of bed was enough energy
OL,17,Fthat I could expel, to the point where
OL,18,FI needed help to get to the toilet.
