OL,6,FThere are roughly 350 believed to be
OL,7,Fliving with ME on the island, and this
OL,8,Fweek marks a year since the clinic was
OL,9,Flaunched.
OL,11,FSpeaking on the stigma surrounding
OL,12,Fchronic fatigue, Thomase said: "If
OL,13,Fpeople actually understand it better,
OL,14,Fthen it's a lot easier to manage.
OL,16,F"The team at Manx Care offer a
OL,17,Fspecialised service to those living
OL,18,Fwith ME, long Covid and chronic
OL,19,Ffatigue syndrome.
